imdb.plot outline: My Beautiful Pain is an original digital series about the careers and relationships within a group of millennial women of color determined to make their mark as the first minority owned LGBT network. Based in Tampa, FL. Tory and her best friends Kacey and Moe come face to face with hardships personally and professionally. Touching on race, sexuality, relationships, family, entrepreneurship, social and economic matters.
